<p>
<seg id=1> According to the ground staff monitoring the hot-balloon's flight around the earth, the three pilots in the hot-balloon should fly out of the territorial sky of China on Wednesday, and then fly eastwards over the Pacific Ocean. </seg>
<seg id=2> On Tuesday, the three-person hot-balloon team encountered political trouble when the hot balloon flew off the planned course. </seg>
<seg id=3> The Chinese officials had ordered them to land in Tibet within the jurisdiction of China, but later China cancelled the order after negotiations with British and American foreign officials. </seg>
